post_text:
Yesterday was the ORES Regional @ Holly Creek. Congratulations to all the winners.

Karli Albert shot put champion, discus champion;
Kara Albert high jump champion, 1600m champion;
Ryleigh Pierce 1600m 3rd place;
Sophie Pulice 400m 3rd place;
Brinklee Butler 100m hurdles 2nd place, 300m hurdles champion;
Hannah Enkoff 800m 2nd place;
Jazzlyn Harrison long jump 4th place;
Ty Holt 800m 3rd place; Girls 4X100m relay 2nd place;
Boys 4X100m relay 4th place;
Girls 4X200m relay 3rd place,
Boys 4X200m relay 3rd place;
Girls 4X400m relay champions.

The Shady Point Girls Track Team was also 3rd over all.

